## Overall Security Assessment

| Area | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| JWT Authentication | ✅ Secure | Correctly validated; invalid/tampered tokens rejected |
| Token Rotation | ✅ Fixed | Bug patched — reuse now properly rejected |
| Token Blacklisting | ✅ Secure | Redis-backed blacklist works for logout and rotation |
| RBAC | ✅ Secure | All role restrictions correctly enforced |
| Rate Limiting | ✅ Secure | 5-attempt lockout triggers correctly; informative 429 response |
| Password Hashing | ✅ Secure | Argon2id (OWASP 2026 recommended) |
| Input Validation | ✅ Secure | Pydantic rejects malformed payloads; SQL injection safe via ORM |
| Inactive Accounts | ✅ Secure | Deactivated users cannot log in |

